{
    "story_id": "",
    "story_name": "龙血之主 各自的道路",
    "story_icon": "",
    "outline": {
        "title": [
            "剧情概要"
        ],
        "content": [
            "一行艰难地击败了阿尔贝琉斯复制体。\\n王族兄弟姐妹们各自下定决心，\\n要继承真正的阿尔贝琉斯的意志，\\n为了超越他的理想而齐心协力\\n面对今后的战斗。"
        ]
    },
    "story_content": [
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09",
                "100054_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "二人",
            "context": "哈啊啊啊啊！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22904_06_0001",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100031_04"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "阿尔贝琉斯复制体",
            "context": "哈啊……哈啊……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22904_06_0002",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100017_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "艾缪尔",
            "context": "呀啊啊啊啊啊啊！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22904_06_0003",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100031_04"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "阿尔贝琉斯复制体",
            "context": "唔！？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22904_06_0004",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100013_05"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱昂尼多",
            "context": "趁现在！巴尔库斯！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22904_06_0005",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100016_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "巴尔库斯",
            "context": "噢噢噢噢噢噢噢！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22904_06_0006",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100031_04"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "阿尔贝琉斯复制体",
            "context": "唔……不错……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22904_06_0007",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100014_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔艾斯",
            "context": "破坏掉核心了。\\n这下终于结束了。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22904_06_0008",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100031_04"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "阿尔贝琉斯复制体",
            "context": "这就是阿尔贝里亚的……\\n我的子孙后代吗……\\n终于可以安心了……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22904_06_0009",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100017_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "艾缪尔",
            "context": "什么终于可以安心了啊？\\n你不会……\\n还有什么别的阴谋吧！？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22904_06_0010",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100014_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔艾斯",
            "context": "不，我已经感觉到他体内的\\n黑暗魔力消失了……现在的他\\n应该不会再打算与我们战斗了。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22904_06_0011",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100014_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔艾斯",
            "context": "没有了黑暗魔力的影响，\\n他现在是真正的阿尔贝琉斯。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22904_06_0012",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100031_04"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "阿尔贝琉斯",
            "context": "抱歉了，我的子孙们啊……\\n是我把太多东西强加在了\\n你们的身上。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22904_06_0013",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100031_04"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "阿尔贝琉斯",
            "context": "若是我能自己\\n把这一些都解决就好了。\\n但现实似乎并不能如我的意……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22904_06_0014",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100016_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "巴尔库斯",
            "context": "阿尔贝琉斯……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22904_06_0015",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100031_04"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "阿尔贝琉斯",
            "context": "你们做得很好。\\n有你们在，这世界定然能够\\n迎来我所未曾实现的未来……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22904_06_0016",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100031_04"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "阿尔贝琉斯",
            "context": "你们都不是孤身一人在战斗……\\n更没有必要以我为榜样……\\n你们应该已经明白这一点了吧？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22904_06_0017",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100016_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "巴尔库斯",
            "context": "嗯。我不会成为第二个阿尔贝琉斯。\\n沿着你所开辟的道路重走一遍\\n没有任何意义。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22904_06_0018",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100016_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "巴尔库斯",
            "context": "我们会继承你的意志，\\n开辟一条我们自己的道路……\\n超越你的理想的道路！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22904_06_0019",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100031_04"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "阿尔贝琉斯",
            "context": "呵……这样啊。\\n那接下来就交给你们了……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22904_06_0020",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100013_05"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱昂尼多",
            "context": "交给我们吗……\\n哼，这自然不用你说。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22904_06_0021",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100017_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "艾缪尔",
            "context": "哎呀～不管怎么说，\\n这下总算是告一段落了吧？\\n这种事我可不想再来第二次了……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22904_06_0022",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100015_06"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "谢斯",
            "context": "哎呀，你在说什么呢？\\n和“起始之人”的对决\\n离结束还远着呢。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22904_06_0023",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100013_05"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱昂尼多",
            "context": "是啊。\\n因为这点事情就叫苦连天的话，\\n接下来可有得担心的了。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22904_06_0024",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100014_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔艾斯",
            "context": "呵呵呵……看来有必要\\n从现在开始重新锻炼你一番了。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22904_06_0025",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100017_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "艾缪尔",
            "context": "我、我已经是狄涅尔帝国的皇帝了！\\n就算是哥哥姐姐你们\\n也不能再命令我！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22904_06_0026",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100013_05"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱昂尼多",
            "context": "是吗。\\n那我现在就把你的皇位夺来好了。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22904_06_0027",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100017_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "艾缪尔",
            "context": "别、别啊！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22904_06_0028",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100015_06"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "谢斯",
            "context": "好啦好啦，王兄。\\n玩笑话不要说太多了，\\n不然他也太可怜了。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22904_06_0029",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100017_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "艾缪尔",
            "context": "是、是在开玩笑……吗？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22904_06_0030",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100015_06"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "谢斯",
            "context": "你的统治地位差不多也稳定下来了。\\n现在再去换皇帝也没有什么意义，\\n只会撒下纷争的火种。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22904_06_0031",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100016_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "巴尔库斯",
            "context": "艾缪尔已经很不容易了。\\n毕竟从结果来讲，是我们抛弃了\\n狄涅尔帝国和那里的民众。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22904_06_0032",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100016_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "巴尔库斯",
            "context": "但能在前任皇帝消失后\\n把混乱控制在这么小的范围，\\n说到底还是因为有人接管了皇帝之位。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22904_06_0033",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100014_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔艾斯",
            "context": "的确，如果没有艾缪尔，\\n我们兄弟几个肯定会被当成\\n弃国而逃的胆小鬼而饱受指责。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22904_06_0034",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100014_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔艾斯",
            "context": "这一点我们还要向你道谢呢。\\n谢谢你，艾缪尔。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22904_06_0035",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100017_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "艾缪尔",
            "context": "哥哥们在向我道谢？\\n怎么回事……是做梦吗？不对，\\n就算是在梦里也不可能有这种好事！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22904_06_0036",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100017_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "艾缪尔",
            "context": "哈！？你们这帮家伙不会都是\\n和那个阿尔贝琉斯一样的冒牌货吧！\\n我可不会上当的！哼哼！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22904_06_0037",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100009_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "塞西娅",
            "context": "艾、艾缪尔哥哥！？\\n你冷静一下！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22904_06_0038",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100013_05"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱昂尼多",
            "context": "你不要会错意了，蠢货。\\n我只是在说因为欠了你一个人情，\\n所以暂时观察你的表现而已。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22904_06_0039",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100013_05"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱昂尼多",
            "context": "不过，邻国情势不稳定的话\\n对我们也会有影响。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22904_06_0040",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100013_05"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱昂尼多",
            "context": "为了防止这样的事情发生，\\n我会亲自教育你何为统治者。\\n你给我做好心理准备。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22904_06_0041",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100017_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "艾缪尔",
            "context": "结、结果还是要这样啊～",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22904_06_0042",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "没事的，艾缪尔。\\n只要我们兄弟姐妹齐心协力，\\n任何困难都不在话下。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22904_06_0043",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100017_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "艾缪尔",
            "context": "也是，只要我们兄弟姐妹齐心协力……\\n哎不对！为什么只有我\\n又要被锻炼又要被教育啊！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22904_06_0044",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100016_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "巴尔库斯",
            "context": "不如我也来帮忙锻炼你吧。\\n毕竟这种事比起一个人，\\n还是人越多效果越好。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22904_06_0045",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100017_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "艾缪尔",
            "context": "连巴尔库斯哥哥你也！？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22904_06_0046",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100014_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔艾斯",
            "context": "（只要兄弟姐妹齐心协力……\\n是啊，今后我也要……）",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22904_06_0048",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100014_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔艾斯",
            "context": "好了，我们该出发了。\\n相信我们的可能性，\\n向我们各自的未来出发吧。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22904_06_0049",
            "book_image": ""
        }
    ]
}